EN: His choices are always so elusive.

ZH: 这个故事中的真相总是不可捉摸。
EN: The truth in this story is always elusive.

ZH: 时间就像一个不可捉摸的流逝之影。
EN: Time is like an elusive passing shadow.

ZH: 她的个性是如此不可捉摸，让人捉摸不透。
EN: Her personality is so elusive that it is unfathomable.

